<p>The NSW Design System is a single source of truth for the design and development of digital things in 
NSW Government. Our mission is to help teams build products and services that meet user needs and deliver great user experiences.</p>
<p>Embracing a code first approach, all aspects of the design system have been built in alignment to deliver simple and consistent user experiences.</p>
<p>Creating experiences from a single, best practice base ensures consistency with how our users engage and interact with NSW Government digitally. Meaning easy to use products and services.</p>

